    stable 0.7.31 0.7.30 0.7.26
   require BeautifulSoup ImageMagick Imaging PyQt4 chmlib cssutils dbus-python lxml mechanize  podofo poppler-qt-x11-opensource python-dateutil setuptools xdg-utils
